@NODE "Mail_0" "[Fwd: Off Topic! SETI@home]"
Date: Fri, 17 Sep 1999 11:32:52 -0500
From: "Robert R Mason" <rrmason@hti.com>
Organization: Raytheon Training Inc.
X-Accept-Language: en
Subject: [Fwd: Off Topic! SETI@home]
 boundary="------------59ED51F9B4D1EC2E0F03420F"
