 Just check the RamBus of a 1200 with a decent accelerator in it, like
an 030+ with fast on it. Try with an old 3D game on AGA. They can run
quite well as a plain machine, but crap out with an accelerator. Also,
a PPC accelerator may need extra power coming in through the Disk drive
port, or it can crash through lack of power (even with a good PSU), as
the main power connectors are weak :/

