--BOUNDARY.1748693536.1

Hi Anton, and Everybody else...

On 25-Oct-99, Anton Reinauer wrote:

>  I don't crawl!! :)
> 
> Cya- Ants Reinauer

Sorry, Ants - but here's more  ;)


Here's what I've managed so far -

Two questions:

1} Does it work on your systems?  (Especially GFX cards?)

2} Any improvements, or any obvious mistakes?


Thanks...

-- 


                                    Yours electronically,
                                    Curt Esser
                                    camge@ix.netcom.com
                                    http://members.xoom.com/Curt_Esser/


--BOUNDARY.1748693536.1
Content-Disposition: attachment; filename="ants.test.asc"


;you'll need amigalibs.res

FindScreen 0
Window 0,0,0,320,180,$100e,"Crawling Ants",-1,-1

*Windo.Window = Peek.l(Addr Window(0))
*Windo\RPort\AreaPtSz = 3

SetDrMd_ *Windo\RPort,2   ;inverse drawing

Left.w  = 100
Right.w = 200
Top.w   = 20
Bottom.w= 111

delay.w=8

Repeat

  *Windo\RPort\AreaPtrn = ?Ants2+offset.w
  BltPattern_ *Windo\RPort,0,Left ,Top   ,Right,Top   ,0
  BltPattern_ *Windo\RPort,0,Left ,Top   ,Left ,Bottom,0

  *Windo\RPort\AreaPtrn = ?Ants+offset.w
  BltPattern_ *Windo\RPort,0,Left ,Bottom,Right,Bottom,0

  *Windo\RPort\AreaPtrn = ?Ants2+offset+1
  BltPattern_ *Windo\RPort,0,Right,Top   ,Right,Bottom,0

  Delay_(delay)

  *Windo\RPort\AreaPtrn = ?Ants2+offset.w
  BltPattern_ *Windo\RPort,0,Left ,Top   ,Right,Top   ,0
  BltPattern_ *Windo\RPort,0,Left ,Top   ,Left ,Bottom,0

  *Windo\RPort\AreaPtrn = ?Ants+offset.w
  BltPattern_ *Windo\RPort,0,Left ,Bottom,Right,Bottom,0

  *Windo\RPort\AreaPtrn = ?Ants+offset+1
  BltPattern_ *Windo\RPort,0,Right,Top   ,Right,Bottom,0

  offset+2
  If offset=14 Then offset=0

Until Event=$200

End

Ants:
Dc.w %1111000011110000
Dc.w %1110000111100001
Dc.w %1100001111000011
Dc.w %1000011110000111
Dc.w %0000111100001111
Dc.w %0001111000011110
Dc.w %0011110000111100
Dc.w %0111100001111000
Dc.w %1111000011110000
Dc.w %1110000111100001
Dc.w %1100001111000011
Dc.w %1000011110000111
Dc.w %0000111100001111
Dc.w %0001111000011110
Dc.w %0011110000111100
Dc.w %0111100001111000

Ants2:

Dc.w %1111000011110000
Dc.w %0111100001111000
Dc.w %0011110000111100
Dc.w %0001111000011110
Dc.w %0000111100001111
Dc.w %1000011110000111
Dc.w %1100001111000011
Dc.w %1110000111100001
Dc.w %1111000011110000
Dc.w %0111100001111000
Dc.w %0011110000111100
Dc.w %0001111000011110
Dc.w %0000111100001111
Dc.w %1000011110000111
Dc.w %1100001111000011
Dc.w %1110000111100001




