> That's my plan.   What is the equivalent code using the Task NewType?
> *MyTask.Task = FindTask_(0) then what?

Right, its like this:

*MyProc.Process = FindTask_(0)
If *MyProc
    *cli.CommandLineInterface = *MyProc\pr_CLI * 4
    If *cli
        If *cli\cli_CommandName
            a$=Peek$(*cli\cli_CommandName + 1)
        End If
    End If
End If

If you're trying to get the name of the program when running from CLI. I can't 
remember cos I deleted the original post.


