Ah, that's easy, they're called logo.sys, logow.sys and other likewise
strange names, I can't remember them, because I deleted them all... Anyway,
just rename them (or a copy of them) with the file extension .bmp and load
them up in your favorite art package, I suggest PPaint, but be warned,
they're in a totally strange format (320*480) if I remember correctly. And
on the subj. of customizing W98, check out LiteStep at
http://www.litestep.org man would I kill for something like this on the
AMiGA.....


