How are you trying to display the colours? You understahnd 16bit and
other high colour displays don`t use palettes?
 
> Say I want Blue it would greenish colour strange.  I know there is noting
> wrong with my BVision as when I display something in 15/16/24Bit displays
> TVPaint there is no problems with the colours.

If you underastand that your 15/16/24bit display doesn`t use a palette
like the old <8but modes then your next problem will be finding the
correct pixel format to render your pixels with.

> Do any of you have source with will work on 8/15/16/24Bit displays.

I don`t know anyone who has done true colour code in Blitz but it's
only because not many people have tried. It's quite easy really, once
you understand how it works.

Cheers,

Paul

