@NODE "Mail_301" "Graphic Scaling"
From: Curt Esser <camge@ix.netcom.com>
Date: Tue, 21 Sep 1999 03:41:08 -0500
Subject: Graphic Scaling
X-UIDL: 0267cf9c8c3f05144150b8fad559833f

--BOUNDARY.1748183008.1

Hi Everybody,

I've attached the beginnings of my current project for testing.  I'd
especially like to know if it works on GFX cards.

It loads pictures using Leigh Perry's datatype functions, then sends them to
a WB window where you can resize them in various ways.

You'll need ReqTools, OS 3, and datatypes installed for the images you want
to load.

Thanks...

Later...
-- 

                                    Yours electronically,
                                    Curt Esser
                                    camge@ix.netcom.com
                                    http://members.xoom.com/Curt_Esser/


--BOUNDARY.1748183008.1
