Hi Sami <sami.naatanen@dlc.fi>,

> *This shouldn't be bold*, *but* *this* *should*
> 
> And turn of the textstyles to see the difference. (Right Amiga + t)

It appears both bold. And heres why. ANYTHING enclosed within *'s is bold, not
just singular words. THis is mentioned in the YAM docs. 

Like this:

*this should be bold because its surrounded by stars*
*this part should be bold* but this part shouldn't.

Etc. Turn off textstyles to see the difference. 

Cya d00d
GazChap.
