@NODE "Mail_334" "HELP - Monitor's blown"
From: Albert Hunt <apthunt@ukonline.co.uk>
Date: Sat, 25 Sep 1999 21:16:59 +0000
Subject: HELP - Monitor's blown
X-UIDL: 17a71b5386e996bc5c17c1549cee33b0

Hello,

Due to a power surge, (Lightning) my monitor has just blown.

I have an old Micro Vetec Cub monitor (connected to a BBC micro)

Does any body know the wiring details of that monitor.

the actual connector is a six pin one :-

                  /-U-\
                 |o   o|
                 |  o  |
                 |o   o|
                 \  o /
                  ----
Well roughly.

I'm sending this from a friend's place, due to this prob.


Any help would be appreciated

Send any replies to the list or to apthunt@ukonline.co.uk
and i can read them.

Thanks

Kind regards

   Leigh



