@ENDNODE
@NODE "Mail_339" "Re: help converting C loop to Blitz loop"
Sender: tdc98@doc.ic.ac.uk
Date: Thu, 28 Oct 1999 17:05:34 +0100
From: Thomas Cobb <tdc98@doc.ic.ac.uk>
X-Accept-Language: en
Subject: Re: help converting C loop to Blitz loop
Encoding: 7bit
X-UIDL: 142276f18ad5de450e698eca9f68a17a

Roger Light wrote:

> Leigh Parry wrote:
>
> > for( i = 0UL ; i < numcolors ; i++ )
>

Literally:

For i.l = 0 To (numcolors-1) Step 1
...
Next i

But you can miss out the Step 1

    Thom


