> In the message sent by the ML server, there are all the infos to get
> some past post. But they need to be referenced by a number, as "post
> 1439 to 1498", you see. How can I know this number ?

If you look at the full headers for the messages, they are contained 
in the return path (thats what it looks like anyway). This message 
will be round about number 14628.

