Hi Andrew <abruno@zeta.org.au>,

On the 18-Sep-99 you muttered something about IRC chat room if I remember correctly, so I thought I would reply! Nice of me wasn't it?

> Could anyone tell me if there is an IRC for discussing BLITZ and what time
> is it busy...  GMT will do.

Well there is, but it kind of declined in popularity after Paul West left. Its
#blitz on irc.esper.net (port 6667) and is mostly busy around 8-11pm BST (GMT+1)

Not a lot of peeple turn up tho. 

Cya d00d
GazChap.
