Hello jean
> hi,
> 
>    this is my two new programm:
>     - one for test the number of entry that we can add with no crash

Nice!!

>     - one for reply to Rob hutchinson 
>       the modification of an entry is done (but i think that is not the
>        more simple solution, because the lenght of the entry is fix)

Yeah... Only you/we have an even bigger problem... It leaks fastmem VERY
VERY badly.. I think it`s cos those Vec`s dont get freed on exit..
Infact, I think they are forgotten about once inserted?
Even when you add five entries, then delete them all and quit you still
lose about 10K of fast. And even more in some situations.
Thats with 5 entries, imagine if there was 1000 entries :(

MUI problems, dont you just love`em?

