@NODE "Mail_507" "NEW Save_IFF Function"
From: Leigh Parry <lparry@ukonline.co.uk>
Date: Fri, 22 Oct 1999 07:23:01 +0000
Subject: NEW Save_IFF Function
X-UIDL: 8b526fe339acc3505967d79e0c009bf6

Warning: This is a message in MIME format. Your mail reader does not
