@NODE "Mail_514" "Newtypes & MaxLen"
From: Roger Light <rogerlight@mindless.com>
Date: Wed, 06 Oct 1999 01:17:32 GMT
Subject: Newtypes & MaxLen
X-UIDL: ea5c98300c8e143d77e0457e8bfb0b51

Hi all,

When using strings in newtypes is there any way of, or any point to, 
defining the MaxLen of all of the strings in it?

As in:

newtype.example
    sausage$
    egg.w
end newtype

dim breakfast.example(100)

Alternatively, how do I make Sizeof.newtype take into account the length of
strings?

Cheers,

Roger
