@NODE "Mail_524" "Re: NListview"
From: =?iso-8859-1?Q?Fr=E9d=E9ric?= Laboureur <alphasnd@sdv.fr>
Date: Mon, 25 Oct 1999 09:49:57 +0100
Subject: Re: NListview
Encoding: 8bit
X-UIDL: a5063daeab5ab03cbb2d3ca60d49ffa1

  Hello Bippy,

> I want to convert one of my proggies over to use Fred's NCS libs.. but I
> am unsure how to detach a list and re-attach to a Nlistview type.. Any
> ideas?
> 
> I need to detach the list, modify it, then re-attach it later?

    Why do you need to modify it ? Just add an item in the list() and the
change will be reflected immediately.

    If you want to change the position/dimension of the listview, just use
the combo NDetachGadgetList()/NAttachGadgetList().
    
        See you,

-- 

