    Hello,

What seems to be the problem with using NLists in MUI using the EFMUILib =
that me
and Erwan Fouret (lib coder) brought to the blitz world? I've used them =
in blitz without
any problems. Included at the 2 included files with constants n stuff =
used for NLists
and NListview. I have also included 3 pictures of an email program that =
is partialy
developed by me (only requires the actuall pop3/smtp functions), and it =
shows you
that I've used the NList and NListview custom class.

Oh one more thing. If someone decides to bitch about the size of this =
email then, to
my defense (?!) i would like to say that I havnt poste danything here in =
ages, so I've
been saving up (?!) my kb credits and used them in this email. So rather =
then droping
in 2-3 emails in the 3kb size area each or everyday, I send one bigger =
email once,
hehe =3D)

 Cyaz



