But what is all this fear of and opposition to oblivion? What
is the matter with the soft darkness, the dreamless sleep?
-- James Thurber

--BOUNDARY.1748211160.2
Content-Disposition: attachment; filename="ADivB.asc"
Content-Description: Can "a" be divided by "b"?


Function.b ADivB {a.f, b.l}

  If b=0 Then Function Return 0 ; no Divide By Zero errors here ;)

; See if value a is divisible by value b
  If Frac (a/b)=0 Then Function Return -1

End Function

Print "Enter number to round to (eg. 2, 5, 10, etc.) : ":round.l=Edit(10)

loop

Print "Enter cents (or -1 to end) : ":cents.l=Edit(10)

If ADivB {cents,round}
  NPrint " * ",cents," is divisible by ",round," *"
Else NPrint " * ",cents," is not divisible by ",round," *"
EndIf

If cents=-1 Then End

Goto loop


--BOUNDARY.1748211160.2

