@NODE "Mail_679" "Rubber-band"
From: Curt Esser <camge@ix.netcom.com>
Date: Sat, 25 Sep 1999 18:17:42 -0500
Subject: Rubber-band
X-UIDL: 30bca8771a04f138793bbdc11e0f6af2

Hi all,

When you "press" on the size gadget of a window and drag it around to
re-size the window, Intuition draws a "rubber-band" as you go to show what
the new size will be.

Does anyone know how to get the current size or co-ordinates of the
rubber-band?

While you are still moving, I mean, before you "release" the size gadget.

Thanks... 

Later...
-- 


                                    Yours electronically,
                                    Curt Esser
                                    camge@ix.netcom.com
                                    http://members.xoom.com/Curt_Esser/



