My only guess as to why you'd want these dimensions is so you can limit the size
the user drags to (?), in which case, you've got SizeLimits (for windows to
follow), or WindowLimits_ () for any specified window (-pointer), which'll
work immediately...

Unless you have some other mysterious reason for wanting this...?

