ZimZum churned out *this* drivel:

> I dunno if I'm doing something wrong here, but is there bugs in
> Savebitmap and savepalette?
 
> If I save bitmaps out from my program, they won't load back in to
> another.. And PPaint, Dpaint, Fastview and Multiview (in fact any pic
