>     Does someone, know the faster method for moving 30 shapes of 32*32
pixel
> max in a 256, or 128 cols screen with a background picture on a 030/50
Mhrz
>
> an example was very good
>
> Thanks

It depends upon whether you`re doing it in Blitz mode or Amiga mode.  In
Blitz mode, it would depend upon whether the shapes are to be 16 bit
aligned - if so, you could use the BLOCK command.  I haven`t tried anything
graphical in Amiga mode, so I can`t comment on that score, except maybe to
use the Scroll commands.

VIC




