HiYa all

Right, I have two questions that I hope someone can possibly
answer (pretty please :)

 1. How do you get a blitz compiled program path and
filename into a string variable? I used to have two
commands called ProgPath$ and ProgName$ that did this for
me a while back, however I lost them when I re-created my
DefLibs. Anyone know a work around for this? Anyone know
which library these commands came from? 

2. Anyone know how to lock and unlock workbench colour or
"pens"? Also, how do I identify which are available for
use?

Thanks for all your help, Thanks to Curt Esser as well for
helping me out with the GTText problem I had. cheers dude,
I never got round to thanking you! :)

