Hello everyone

On 15-Sep-99, Matt Briggs shared his opinion:

> 2. Anyone know how to lock and unlock workbench colour or
> "pens"? Also, how do I identify which are available for
> use?

Try using ObtainPen_() or ObtainBestPen_() for locking and ReleasePen_() for
unlocking.

Kind regards from Slovenia
